  "description": "Sprout & Soil is a farming expansion mod that adds a wide variety of new crops, ingredients, and food recipes to Minecraft",
  "body": "<!-- HEADER -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vrZ6ThO.png\" alt=\"Sprout & Soil mod banner showing crops and fresh vegetables in Minecraft style\">\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative divider line\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- SOCIALS -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" \n             alt=\"Join the NightBeam Studio Discord server\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@nightbeamstudio\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\" \n             alt=\"Watch NightBeam Studio YouTube channel\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\" \n             alt=\"Support NightBeam Studio on GitHub Sponsors\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\" \n             alt=\"NightBeam Studio on CurseForge\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\" \n             alt=\"NightBeam Studio on Modrinth\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative divider line\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- ABOUT HEADER -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" alt=\"About section header\">\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M8UPZoW.png\" alt=\"Sprout & Soil icon illustration\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- ABOUT TEXT -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <strong>About Sprout & Soil:</strong><br>\n    Sprout & Soil is a farming-focused Minecraft mod that adds a large variety of new crops, plants, and ingredients. \n    Players can grow tomatoes, berries, and other crops, then craft exciting new food recipes. The mod enhances farming, \n    cooking, and exploration, giving survival worlds more variety, creativity, and a sense of progression.\n</p>\n\n<!-- WHY CHOOSE -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <strong>Why Choose Sprout & Soil?</strong><br>\n    - Expand your farming possibilities with dozens of unique crops.<br>\n    - Unlock new crafting and cooking mechanics.<br>\n    - Enjoy visually appealing crops and plants with high-quality textures.<br>\n    - Benefit from a mod that receives frequent updates and community feedback.\n</p>\n\n<!-- KO-FI -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" \n             style=\"width:220px;\" \n             alt=\"Support NightBeam Studio on Ko-Fi to help fund mod development\">\n    </a>\n    <span style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\">Support NightBeam Studio on Ko-Fi to help fund mod development and updates.</span>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative divider line\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- FEATURES HEADER -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" alt=\"Features section header\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- FEATURES LIST -->\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>New Tomato Plant & Seeds:</strong> Grow fresh tomato plants and use them in recipes.</li>\n    <li><strong>Expanded Farming Content:</strong> Additional crops, plants, and ingredients are coming soon.</li>\n    <li><strong>New Foods & Recipes:</strong> Craft flavorful meals from your harvest.</li>\n    <li><strong>Ongoing Updates:</strong> The mod receives regular updates adding new farming mechanics and items.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- ROADMAP -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <strong>Roadmap & Future Updates:</strong><br>\n    - New crops like peppers, melons, and exotic fruits.<br>\n    - Farm animals and new livestock mechanics.<br>\n    - Seasonal crops and dynamic farming events.<br>\n    - Cooking expansions with special recipes and effects.\n</p>\n\n<!-- INSTALLATION -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative divider line\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" alt=\"Installation section header\">\n</p>\n\n<div>\n    <p><strong>⏩ Supported Versions:</strong> 1.20.1</p>\n    <p><strong>⏩ Requires:</strong> NeoForge or Forge</p>\n    <p><strong>⏩ Also Requires:</strong> JAUMl Library</p>\n    <p><strong>⏩ How to Install:</strong> Drop the mod .jar file into your Minecraft mods folder and launch with the correct Forge/NeoForge version.</p>\n</div>\n",
